In the Terraform HCL for the opcert key SSM parameter:
```hcl
resource "aws_ssm_parameter" "opcert_ed25519_key" {
  name  = "/rebar/prod/opcert-ed25519-key"
  type  = "SecureString"
  value = "CHANGEME"

  lifecycle {
    ignore_changes  = [value]
    prevent_destroy = true   # key exists nowhere else — accidental destroy is irrecoverable
  }
}
```
Update AC1 to assert: `terraform show -json tf.plan` shows `prevent_destroy = true` on this resource.

